thread.title: North Korea Is Off to the Winter Olympics, but Who Will Go?

author: Sara Germano
title: North Korea Is Off to the Winter Olympics, but Who Will Go?
text:
Following North Korea’s agreement to send a delegation to the Winter Olympics, it still isn’t clear which athletes from the North will attend next month’s Games in Pyeongchang, South Korea.
The pairs figure-skating team of Ryom Tae Ok and Kim Ju Sik earned a berth for North Korea last fall, but they missed a registration deadline to declare their intent to compete in Pyeongchang.
